MALACAÑANG

RESIDENCE OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE PHILIPPINES MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 469-B

EXCLUDING FROM THE OPERATION OF PROCLAMATION NO. 687 DATED JULY 15, 1960, WHICH ESTABLISHED THE RELOCATION SITE RESERVATION FOR INDIGENT SQUATTERS, FLOOD VICTIMS AND OTHER INDIGENTS OF GREATER MANILA, CERTAIN PORTIONS OF THE LAND EMBRACED THEREIN AND DECLARING THE SAME OPEN TO DISPOSITION IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE PROVISIONS OF REPUBLIC ACT NUMBERED FOUR HUNDRED AND SEVENTY SEVEN.

By virtue of powers vested in me by law, I, Diosdado Macapagal, President of the Philippines, do hereby exclude from the operation of Proclamation No. 687, dated July 15, 1960, which establish the relocation site reservation for the indigent squatters, flood victims and other indigent of Greater Manila, situated along J. Posadas Jr. Road, Punta, City of Manila, certain portions of the land embraced therein and declare the same open disposition in accordance with the provisions of Republic Act Numbered Four Hundred and Seventy-seven, as amended, which portions are more particularly described as follows:

Boundary Technical Description

A parcel of land (Consolidated boundaries of Lots 1 to 13, Block 1; Lots 1 to 26, Block 2; Lots 1 to 34, Block 4; Lots 1 to 18, Block 5 Lots 1 to 6, Block 6; Block 7 and Road Lots 1 to 2 (LRC) Fes-193, being a portion of the consolidation of Lots 2 and 3, Fcs- 3493, LRC (GLRO) Record Nos. 4434 and 52842), situated in the District of Sta. Ana, City of Manila island of Luzon. Bounded on the NE., points 9 to 12 by Lot 3 points 12 to 13 by Lot 2; points 13 to 15 by Lot 1, all of Block 3, (LRC) Pex-193; points 16 to 17 by Lot 2, Rs-264; and points 7 to 20, by property of Philippine Match Co., ltd.; on the SE., points 20 to 31 by Lot 5, Block 1, Rs-264, Swo-18237) property of Gregorio Araneta Inc.; points 1 to 2 by Lot 6-B-2B, Psd-32211, property of Marcelo Steel Corporation; on the SW., points 31 to 33 by Lot 6-Z-1, Block 1, Swo-18237, property of Gregorio Araneta Inc., and points 33 to 1 by Lot 1-B-2-B, Psd-32211 property of Marcelo Steel Corporation ; points 2 to 4 by Lot 1, Pcs-3493, property of the Republic of the Philippines; and on the NW., points 4 to 9 by Pasig River. Beginning at a point marked 1 on plan, being N. 51 deg. 44 min. W., 618.68 m. from Sta. Ana Church Spire,

